{"tid":2023680,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(回帶)作文撰「飛魚巴菲特」 考生瘀爆","createTime":"2020-05-19T06:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T06:59:44.000Z","uid":39206,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dbcd0fff2021c286273ac6e26bad87fd833e0863","tid":2023680,"uid":39206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:59:44.000Z","msg":"好過宜家d特首，假野當真引用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但有考生在試後接受媒體訪問時指，作答有關「夢想」題目時，<span style=\"color: red;\">以美國游泳健將「巴菲特」作例子答題，並自感發揮不錯，</span>結果被身旁的友人糾正指巴菲特是「股神」，菲比斯才是運動員。<br />\n<a href=\"https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/2015%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E6%96%87%E6%86%91%E8%A9%A6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.org%2Fzh%2Fwiki%2F2015%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2586%2591%25E8%25A9%25A6&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2Fwy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=39dffc96\" target=\"_blank\">https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/2015%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E6%96%87%E6%86%91%E8%A9%A6</a>"}]}